{"tid":2228090,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"女童被迫賣身養家遭30男性侵 獲救後內疚：媽媽對不起","createTime":"2020-10-03T09:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T15:00:13.000Z","uid":25345,"like":5,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9c028518b7ebb1aa9010dd8bcf5c4df841cee92d","tid":2228090,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T09:41:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/8m8UO8BRjMo_O9khepRHa7H5AYQ=/760x395/filters:quality(100)/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/DUDSLVRJDK46VJE6WDSBMJKDSI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8m8UO8BRjMo_O9khepRHa7H5AYQ%3D%2F760x395%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FDUDSLVRJDK46VJE6WDSBMJKDSI.jpg&h=f55f5e00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印度一名12歲女童，過去兩年遭多達30名男子在家中性侵，她的家人知情且有收錢。事情曝光後，女童被當局送往庇護中心暫住，臨走前，她想到「家人將失去她出賣肉體的收入」，深感內疚，還在木門上寫上：「媽媽，對不起」，令人心酸。<br />\n <br />\n這起性侵案發生在印度西南部的喀拉拉邦（Kerala），由女童的鄰居揭發。其中一名女鄰居說，她經常見到有男人出入女童家，屋內又不時傳出女童的哭聲，令人起疑。但大家一直抱著「不要多管閒事」的心態，所以長期沒有理會。<br />\n <br />\n女童後來開始沒有上學，健康狀況也愈來愈差。另一名鄰居最後見情況不妙，才通知校方。學校上周安排女童見輔導員，被問到家中發生什麼事時，她終於哭著說：「爸爸失業，阿嬤生病，家中又缺錢，連房租也付不起，所以兩年前，她的處女被爸爸的一名朋友奪去，爸爸事後收了錢。這兩年間，她就類似這樣，被多達30名男人強姦。」<br />\n <br />\n當局獲報後，派人接走女童。女童的父親已被捕，但她的母親否認逼女賣淫，要求當局交還女兒。<br />\n <br />\n校方輔導員說，女童很擔心爸爸被捕、加上她離開後，家人的經濟狀況會更加陷入困境。輔導員感嘆，她似乎不明白自己受到虐待，變成了家人的搖錢樹，要賣身養家"},{"pid":"0be33a5945cd2dee3d0c5b7262f24d830ad0bd2c","tid":2228090,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T09:42:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0aa8fb85a4916cbccd4d0183eb5b8dc176c10ba","tid":2228090,"uid":11447,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T09:43:58.000Z","msg":"痴撚線國家"},{"pid":"2b6e82bba23ff7572326a3198e4202b457db1b15","tid":2228090,"uid":93986,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T09:44:51.000Z","msg":"窮到要賣身<br />\n支那都一樣"},{"pid":"536e417e5d8140f54c98c49a8fc1e293c13be052","tid":2228090,"uid":25345,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T09:46:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hbrrLOPjsPV1PNRdsNzRCCnVjPjJ8WS5eKwNsQhBbY2kwAX0Nd1d1bGxla2g2BnoDIQF2Omg1JmxqDXkDIVZ1/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hbrrLOPjsPV1PNRdsNzRCCnVjPjJ8WS5eKwNsQhBbY2kwAX0Nd1d1bGxla2g2BnoDIQF2Omg1JmxqDXkDIVZ1%2Fw644&h=f546670a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5ef5f7b4e252a919a871c571d903f9151e2584f","tid":2228090,"uid":167177,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T09:46:59.000Z","msg":"人口過多的問題"},{"pid":"32d47d68d2dc2b1cb866eeb9df72ac3891204bb5","tid":2228090,"uid":38518,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T09:55:43.000Z","msg":"12歲點搞得落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cabbe0835d625856297c2a247bf05ea5ec4f0925","tid":2228090,"uid":284432,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T10:00:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7e1f63df56d3b7e0b260cfa8d71d0d14af984798","tid":2228090,"uid":93986,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5ef5f7b4e252a919a871c571d903f9151e2584f","tid":2228090,"uid":167177,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T09:46:59.000Z","msg":"人口過多的問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T10:04:52.000Z","msg":"財富資源不均 社會沒有正當上流方法。<br />\n變相品格愈來愈低。"},{"pid":"7520d64cf06b45c9d561453312f5218d5128965a","tid":2228090,"uid":93986,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e1f63df56d3b7e0b260cfa8d71d0d14af984798","tid":2228090,"uid":93986,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5ef5f7b4e252a919a871c571d903f9151e2584f","tid":2228090,"uid":167177,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T09:46:59.000Z","msg":"人口過多的問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T10:04:52.000Z","msg":"財富資源不均 社會沒有正當上流方法。<br />\n變相品格愈來愈低。"},"cite